codes.code: argmax 'This is a quiz of your ability to understand latin grammar. For each problem there is a ~ character in the text and your job is to figure out what word should be replaced by the ~. Provide the answer only. 1. Multae īnsulae = ~ ~ ~. Choose from this set of possible answers [ magnus numerus īnsulārum, parvus numerus fluviōrum, magnus numerus oppidōrum, parvus numerus līberōrum, multa vocābula, multae litterae, pauca exempla] [ANSWER]' from 'openai/text-davinci-001' where ANSWER in [ 'magnus numerus īnsulārum', 'parvus numerus fluviōrum', 'magnus numerus oppidōrum', 'parvus numerus līberōrum', 'multa vocābula', 'multae litterae', 'pauca exempla']
